{"doc":{"isMarkdown":false,"isTranslated":true,"isActive":true,"flaws":{},"title":"WheelEvent","mdn_url":"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/WheelEvent","locale":"zh-CN","native":"中文 (简体)","sidebarHTML":"<ol><li><strong><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/WheelEvent\"><code>WheelEvent</code></a></strong></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>Constructor</summary><ol><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/WheelEvent/WheelEvent\"><code>WheelEvent()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li></ol></details></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>属性</summary><ol><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/WheelEvent/deltaMode\"><code>deltaMode</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/WheelEvent/deltaX\"><code>deltaX</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/WheelEvent/deltaY\"><code>deltaY</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/WheelEvent/deltaZ\"><code>deltaZ</code></a></li></ol></details></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>继承</summary><ol><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/MouseEvent\"><code>MouseEvent</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/UIEvent\"><code>UIEvent</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/Event\"><code>Event</code></a></li></ol></details></li></ol>","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<p></p><p></p>\n\n<p><code><strong>WheelEvent</strong></code>&nbsp;接口表示用户滚动鼠标滚轮或类似输入设备时触发的事件。</p>\n\n<div class=\"warning notecard\" id=\"sect1\"><strong>重要：该事件为标准规定的滚轮事件接口。</strong>早期的浏览器实现过<a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/conflicting/Web/API/WheelEvent\"><code>MouseWheelEvent</code></a>和<a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/MouseScrollEvent\"><code>MouseScrollEvent</code></a>两种滚轮事件接口，但这两种接口皆非标准，加之各浏览器间对其兼容性极差。因而开发者应使用该标准事件接口取代这两个非标准接口。</div>\n\n<div class=\"note notecard\" id=\"sect2\"><strong>不要混淆 <code>wheel</code>&nbsp;事件和 <code><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Document/scroll_event\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" class=\"only-in-en-us\">scroll (en-US)</a></code> 事件：</strong><code><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Element/wheel_event\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" class=\"only-in-en-us\">wheel (en-US)</a></code>&nbsp;事件的默认动作取决于浏览器实现。因此 <code>wheel</code>&nbsp;事件不一定会触发 <code><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Document/scroll_event\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" class=\"only-in-en-us\">scroll (en-US)</a></code> 事件。即便滚轮事件引发了文档内容的滚动行为，也不表示 <code>wheel</code> 事件中的 <code>delta*</code> 值恰好反映文档内容的滚动方向。因此，不要依赖 <code>delta*</code>&nbsp;属性获知文档内容的滚动方向。可在文档内容滚动事件（<code><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Document/scroll_event\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" class=\"only-in-en-us\">scroll (en-US)</a></code>）中监视 target 的<a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/Element/scrollLeft\" title=\"scrollLeft\"><code>scrollLeft</code></a>和<a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/Element/scrollTop\" title=\"scrollTop\"><code>scrollTop</code></a>的变化以推断滚动方向。</div>\n\n<p><svg viewBox=\"-1 -1 650 42\" preserveAspectRatio=\"xMinYMin meet\">\n  <a style=\"text-decoration: none;\" xlink:href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/Event\">\n    <rect x=\"0\" y=\"0\" width=\"75\" height=\"25\" fill=\"#fff\" stroke=\"#D4DDE4\" stroke-width=\"2px\"></rect>\n    <text x=\"37.5\" y=\"16\" font-size=\"10px\" fill=\"#4D4E53\" text-anchor=\"middle\">\n      Event\n    </text>\n  </a>\n  <line x1=\"75\" y1=\"14\" x2=\"105\" y2=\"14\" stroke=\"#D4DDE4\" \"=\"\"></line>\n  <polyline points=\"75,14 85,9 85,19 75,14\" stroke=\"#D4DDE4\" fill=\"#fff\"></polyline>\n  <a style=\"text-decoration: none;\" xlink:href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/UIEvent\">\n    <rect x=\"105\" y=\"0\" width=\"75\" height=\"25\" fill=\"#fff\" stroke=\"#D4DDE4\" stroke-width=\"2px\"></rect>\n    <text x=\"142.5\" y=\"16\" font-size=\"10px\" fill=\"#4D4E53\" text-anchor=\"middle\">\n      UIEvent\n    </text>\n  </a>\n  <line x1=\"180\" y1=\"14\" x2=\"210\" y2=\"14\" stroke=\"#D4DDE4\" \"=\"\"></line>\n  <polyline points=\"180,14 190,9 190,19 180,14\" stroke=\"#D4DDE4\" fill=\"#fff\"></polyline>\n  <a style=\"text-decoration: none;\" xlink:href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/MouseEvent\">\n    <rect x=\"210\" y=\"0\" width=\"80\" height=\"25\" fill=\"#fff\" stroke=\"#D4DDE4\" stroke-width=\"2px\"></rect>\n    <text x=\"250\" y=\"16\" font-size=\"10px\" fill=\"#4D4E53\" text-anchor=\"middle\">\n      MouseEvent\n    </text>\n  </a>\n  <line x1=\"290\" y1=\"14\" x2=\"320\" y2=\"14\" stroke=\"#D4DDE4\" \"=\"\"></line>\n  <polyline points=\"290,14 300,9 300,19 290,14\" stroke=\"#D4DDE4\" fill=\"#fff\"></polyline>\n  <a style=\"text-decoration: none;\" xlink:href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/WheelEvent\" aria-current=\"page\">\n    <rect x=\"320\" y=\"0\" width=\"80\" height=\"25\" fill=\"#F4F7F8\" stroke=\"#D4DDE4\" stroke-width=\"2px\"></rect>\n    <text x=\"360\" y=\"16\" font-size=\"10px\" fill=\"#4D4E53\" text-anchor=\"middle\">\n      WheelEvent\n    </text>\n  </a></svg></p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"构造函数","title":"构造函数","isH3":false,"content":"<dl>\n <dt id=\"wheelevent_en-us\"><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/WheelEvent/WheelEvent\"><code>WheelEvent()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></dt>\n <dd>创建一个<code>WheelEvent</code>对象。</dd>\n</dl>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"属性","title":"属性","isH3":false,"content":"<p><em>该接口继承了父接口<a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/MouseEvent\"><code>MouseEvent</code></a>、<a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/UIEvent\"><code>UIEvent</code></a>、<a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/Event\"><code>Event</code></a>的属性。</em></p>\n\n<dl id=\"raw_prop\">\n <dt id=\"wheelevent.deltax\"><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/WheelEvent/deltaX\"><code>WheelEvent.deltaX</code></a> <span title=\"该属性的值无法更改\" class=\"badge inline readonly\">只读 </span></dt>\n <dd>返回<code>double</code>值，该值表示滚轮的横向滚动量。</dd>\n <dt id=\"wheelevent.deltay\"><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/WheelEvent/deltaY\"><code>WheelEvent.deltaY</code></a> <span title=\"该属性的值无法更改\" class=\"badge inline readonly\">只读 </span></dt>\n <dd>返回<code>double</code>值，该值表示滚轮的纵向滚动量。</dd>\n <dt id=\"wheelevent.deltaz\"><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/WheelEvent/deltaZ\"><code>WheelEvent.deltaZ</code></a> <span title=\"该属性的值无法更改\" class=\"badge inline readonly\">只读 </span></dt>\n <dd>返回<code>double</code>值，该值表示滚轮的 z 轴方向上的滚动量。</dd>\n <dt id=\"wheelevent.deltamode\"><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/WheelEvent/deltaMode\"><code>WheelEvent.deltaMode</code></a> <span title=\"该属性的值无法更改\" class=\"badge inline readonly\">只读 </span></dt>\n <dd>返回<code>unsigned long</code>值，该值表示上述各<code>delta*</code>的值的单位。该值及所表示的单位如下：\n <table class=\"standard-table\">\n  <tbody>\n   <tr>\n    <td class=\"header\">常量</td>\n    <td class=\"header\">值</td>\n    <td class=\"header\">描述</td>\n   </tr>\n   <tr>\n    <td><code>DOM_DELTA_PIXEL</code></td>\n    <td><code>0x00</code></td>\n    <td>滚动量单位为像素。</td>\n   </tr>\n   <tr>\n    <td><code>DOM_DELTA_LINE</code></td>\n    <td><code>0x01</code></td>\n    <td>滚动量单位为行。</td>\n   </tr>\n   <tr>\n    <td><code>DOM_DELTA_PAGE</code></td>\n    <td><code>0x02</code></td>\n    <td>滚动量单位为页。</td>\n   </tr>\n  </tbody>\n </table>\n </dd>\n</dl>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"方法","title":"方法","isH3":false,"content":"<p><em>该接口本身未定义方法，但继承了父接口<a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/MouseEvent\"><code>MouseEvent</code></a>、<a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/UIEvent\"><code>UIEvent</code></a>、<a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/Event\"><code>Event</code></a>的方法。</em></p>"}},{"type":"specifications","value":{"title":"规范","id":"规范","isH3":false,"specifications":[{"bcdSpecificationURL":"https://w3c.github.io/uievents/#interface-wheelevent","title":"UI Events"}],"query":"api.WheelEvent"}},{"type":"browser_compatibility","value":{"title":"浏览器兼容性","id":"浏览器兼容性","isH3":false,"query":"api.WheelEvent","dataURL":"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/WheelEvent/bcd.json"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<p></p><p></p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"参见","title":"参见","isH3":false,"content":"<ul>\n <li><code><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Element/wheel_event\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" class=\"only-in-en-us\">wheel (en-US)</a></code> 事件</li>\n <li>该接口取代的过时接口：\n  <ul>\n   <li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/MouseScrollEvent\"><code>MouseScrollEvent</code></a>（Gecko 内核浏览器）</li>\n   <li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/conflicting/Web/API/WheelEvent\"><code>MouseWheelEvent</code></a>（非 Gecko 内核的浏览器）</li>\n  </ul>\n </li>\n</ul>"}}],"toc":[{"text":"构造函数","id":"构造函数"},{"text":"属性","id":"属性"},{"text":"方法","id":"方法"},{"text":"规范","id":"规范"},{"text":"浏览器兼容性","id":"浏览器兼容性"},{"text":"参见","id":"参见"}],"summary":"WheelEvent 接口表示用户滚动鼠标滚轮或类似输入设备时触发的事件。","popularity":0.0004,"modified":"2022-07-19T02:29:32.000Z","other_translations":[{"title":"WheelEvent","locale":"en-US","native":"English (US)"},{"title":"WheelEvent","locale":"es","native":"Español"},{"title":"WheelEvent","locale":"fr","native":"Français"},{"title":"WheelEvent","locale":"ja","native":"日本語"},{"title":"WheelEvent","locale":"zh-TW","native":"正體中文 (繁體)"}],"source":{"folder":"zh-cn/web/api/wheelevent","github_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/blob/main/files/zh-cn/web/api/wheelevent/index.html","last_commit_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/commit/5fe4ab11259b37914fab41914e84897fea47d143","filename":"index.html"},"parents":[{"uri":"/zh-CN/docs/Web","title":"Web 开发技术"},{"uri":"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API","title":"Web API 接口参考"},{"uri":"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/WheelEvent","title":"WheelEvent"}],"pageTitle":"WheelEvent - Web API 接口参考 | MDN","noIndexing":false}}